OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy and cool across parts of
OL,6,Fnorthern England and southern
OL,7,FScotland, with occasional light
OL,8,Fdrizzle. Sunnier to the south across
OL,9,FEngland and Wales, and fine with sunny
OL,10,Fspells elsewhere. Temperatures remain
OL,11,Fabove average, though slightly lower
OL,12,Fthan on Wednesday.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FCloudy for southeast Scotland
OL,15,Fand northeast England, especially near
OL,16,Fcoasts and spreading inland overnight.
OL,17,FElsewhere, clear spells bring a chilly
OL,18,Fnight with some mist and fog patches
OL,19,Fin prone spots.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
