OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FEarly mist or fog clearing
OL,6,Finto a fine, warm day with light
OL,7,Fwinds. Sunshine for most, though the
OL,8,Ffar north and northwest turn cloudier
OL,9,Fand breezier later with patchy rain.
